0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"(g) 低地台巴士的輪椅位置佔用多少面積?可供多少人 站立及是否計入下層&ldquo;企位&rdquo;?<br />\n<br />\n運輸署的回覆<br />\n<br />\n提問(g) :<br />\r低地台巴士車廂內，可供輪椅泊位的面積，不少於 750毫米 x 1300毫米。如輪椅泊位未有被使用，輪椅泊位約可供五位站立 乘客使用。運輸署在計算專營巴士下層企位數目時，會將輪椅 泊位作為企位計算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2012_2015/common/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/3919/st_ttc_2015_020_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fst%2Fdoc%2F2012_2015%2Fcommon%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2Fttc%2F3919%2Fst_ttc_2015_020_tc.pdf&d=YNG%2ByCLZrigdDwYgCyUwpghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=00fba966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2012_2015/common/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/3919/st_ttc_2015_020_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運輸署話企得喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3638f551ef5d74790287348fbc252a41604db86","tid":507484,"uid":148546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"大把香港人都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f28f2fee358487f8881c44d1cf71e26b128977","tid":507484,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"當見過班傻閪放係到唔緊要 綁都唔撚綁由佢撞來撞去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ae7d6a4022c40f64bcd41dca889a78ae39c04e","tid":507484,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3638f551ef5d74790287348fbc252a41604db86","tid":507484,"uid":148546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"大把香港人都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"啲買餸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif